    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In Christi nomine, breve pro moderni et futuri temporis memoria qualis apud
                            <placeName ref="#places/63" key="#Roads">Sanctam Mariam
                            Monte</placeName>, in domo quondam <persName><name ref="Francardinus"
                                >Francardini</name></persName>, prefatus Francardinus quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Paganus">Paganusci</name></persName>, pro se et
                        pro nepote suo <persName><name ref="Bonincontrus"
                            >Bonincontro</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Paltoniere"
                                >Paltonieri</name></persName>, <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"
                            >bonorum hominum</rs> presentia quorum subter leguntur nomina, per
                        virgam quod in sua tenebat manu investivit <persName><name ref="Cantapegium"
                                >Cantapegium</name></persName> ad partem et […] <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">Sancti
                            Gilii</orgName> et <rs key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3207" key="#Churches #Hospitals">Altepascio</placeName> de
                        uno casamento in pede ripa, sito […] <persName><name ref="Paganus"
                                >Paganelli</name></persName>. Et tenet unum capud in <rs
                            key="#Roads">via puplica</rs>, aliud capud cum latere in domo
                        suprascripti Paganelli, que est supramemorati hospitalis, latus aliud in
                        terra del <persName><name ref="Bonragione">Borragioni</name></persName>. Et
                        est a parte orientis. Quatinus supramemoratum hospitale deinceps in antea in
                        perpetuum habeat et detineat, sine omni redditu, pro nostrarum aniamarum
                        (sic) […] pro parentum remedio. Et pro suprascripta investitione
                        confirmanda, hospitale concessit prefato Fracardino edificium cuiusdam case
                        ibi prope. […] Centum pena sol. feriantur. […] Hoc autem actum est <rs
                            key="#Witness">presentia</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Incalzatus"
                                >Incalciati</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> filii, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Andreas/Beveacqua"
                                >Andree</name></persName> qui Beacqua vocatur, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Damianus"
                                >Damamianelli</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Damianus">Damiani</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Baldinellus"
                                >Baldinelli</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Saracinus">Saraceni</name></persName>. Anno dominice
                        incarnationis eius millesimo centesimo quadragesimo quinto, tertio kalendas
                        martii, indictione VIII. (S) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Hughicio">Uguicio</name></persName>, domni imperatoris <rs
                            key="#Writer #Tabellio">tabellio</rs>, his omnibus interfui et causa
                        memorie hoc breve descripsi. </ab>
                </div>
